  <thing id="rauBaShCap" name="Captivating Dance" description="When a baobhan sith dances, all living creatures within 30 feet that view the rhythmic swaying and movements of her body must succeed on a Will save or become utterly enthralled and captivated. Creatures that are sexually attracted to females who view this dance suffer a -2 penalty on their saving throws. A creature that makes its save cannot be affected again by the same baobhan sith&apos;s captivating dance for one day. A captivated creature is dazed (it cannot attack, but can defend normally). This continues for as long as the baobhan sith dances. A baobhan sith can move and act normally (including using her spell-like abilities) while maintaining her dance. The save DC is Charisma-based." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Dance enthralls all within 30 ft.">
