  <thing id="rauAbyHvHv" name="Harvest" description="This ability can only be used when the abyssal harvester is on its abyssal plane and injects its tentacles into the Ethereal Plane, Astral Plane, a material plane, or the Nine Hells.\n\nA grappled foe with 20 or fewer hit points or 4 or fewer Constitution points must succeed on a Will save or be drawn through an invisible planar gate (created around the abyssal harvester&apos;s tentacles) onto the same plane where the abyssal harvester currently resides. An opponent drawn into the same plane with the harvester is still grappled upon arrival. The save DC is Charisma-based." compset="RaceSpec">
