  <thing id="rauAeSLnkC" name="Link with Caster" description="When summoned, an aerial servant creates a mental link between itself and the caster who summoned it. Should the aerial servant fail the mission it has been assigned, it returns to the caster and attacks him. The aerial servant can find the caster as long as they both are on the same plane of existence. If the caster leaves the plane, the link is temporarily broken. Once the caster returns or the aerial servant enters the plane the caster is on, the link is immediately reestablished and the aerial servant moves at full speed toward the caster&apos;s current location. Only when the aerial servant or caster is destroyed, is the link permanently broken." compset="RaceSpec">
