  <thing id="rauBacChmG" name="Charming Gaze" description=" In human form, a baccae&apos;s gaze can charm any creature meeting her gaze and within 30 feet. An affected creature can attempt a DC 14 Will save to resist the effects. If the save fails, the opponent acts as if affected by a charm person spell (caster level equals the baccae&apos;s HD). A baccae can suppress this ability as a free action. The save DC is Charisma-based." compset="RaceSpec">
