  <thing id="rauBsCrBdF" name="Blood Frenzy" description="A crimson basilisk that detects fresh blood within 30 feet enters a frenzied state the following round, along with all other crimson basilisks within 30 feet. Frenzied crimson basilisks fight until they or their opponents are dead. A frenzied crimson basilisk gains a +2 bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls and -2 AC for 1 minute. The creature cannot end the frenzy voluntarily. A crimson basilisk can enter a frenzy only once per encounter." compset="RaceSpec">
