  <thing id="rauBlBhImp" name="Implant" description="A creature hit by one of the blood bush&apos;s flower darts is implanted with one of its seeds. A seed quickly germinates as follows:\n\n1st round: DC 18 Will save or flee in fear for 1d6 rounds\n3rd round: Paralysis for 1d4+2 rounds; DC 18 Fortitude negates\n5th round: Wounding: 1 point of Constitution damage per minute until the seed is removed or destroyed.\n\nA seed can be removed safely up to 5 rounds after implantation with a successful DC 18 Heal check or by cutting it from the victim (dealing 1d2 points of damage); otherwise only a remove disease spell destroys an implanted seed. The save DCs and check DC are Constitution-based." compset="RaceSpec">
