  <thing id="rauBCbBnst" name="Bonestripping" description="A bone cobbler can rapidly strip all the flesh from a Medium creature in 3 minutes using its claws and hammers. For each size category larger than Medium a corpse is, add 1 minute to the time it takes the bone cobbler to strip the corpse. For each size category smaller than Medium a corpse is, reduce the time by 1 minute (to a minimum of 1 minute). Once stripped, the bone cobbler devours the flesh and collects the victim&apos;s bones to use in its “sculptures”.\n\nA creature slain in this manner can only be brought back to life by a miracle, wish, or true resurrection spell." compset="RaceSpec">
