  <thing id="rauCbSkCBr" name="Consume Brain" description="Once it has its victim underground, the cerebral stalker begins gnawing on the victim&apos;s head, rapidly chewing through bone and tissue, dealing 2d8+4 points of damage each round. When the victim dies, the cerebral stalker has reached its goal-the victim&apos;s brain, which it promptly devours. A victim slain in this manner is ejected from the ground and becomes a zombie." compset="RaceSpec">
