  <thing id="rauJdColIM" name="Immunity to Magic" description="A jade colossus is immune to any spell or spell-like ability that allows spell resistance. In addition, certain spells and effects function differently against the creature, as noted below.\n\nA disintegrate spell slows a jade colossus (as the slow spell) for 1d6 rounds, with no saving throw.\n\nA shatter spell deals 3d12 points of damage to a jade colossus, with no saving throw.\n\nA magical attack that deals fire damage breaks any slow effect on the jade colossus and heals 1 point of damage for each 3 points of damage the attack would otherwise deal. If the amount of healing would cause the golem to exceed its full normal hit points, it gains any excess as temporary hit points. A jade colossus gets no saving throw against fire effects." compset="RaceSpec">
