  <thing id="ruDmOozGre" name="Demon, Ooze, Greater" description="Ooze demons are the forgotten children of Jubilex, The Faceless Lord, faithful servants that obey the will of their master without question. When the Faceless Lord went missing the ooze demons formed search parties and scoured the planes for signs of his whereabouts.\n\nOoze demons, both lesser and greater, appear as a combination of ooze and demon. An ooze demon resembles a humanoid with a long, crocodilian snout, razor-sharp teeth, and long talons. From a distance, this monster looks like a typical demon (if such a thing exists). Up close, the horror is easily ascertainable; the creature is actually a single entity of swirling black and white or black and gray ooze in the shape of a humanoid.\n\nGreater ooze demons attack using their slams or bite and claw attacks. They like to grab a foe and hold on, pulling it close to their body where they subject it to their acid damage. They are not afraid of charging straight into melee, as unaware opponents soon discover their weapons dissolve upon contacting the demon&apos;s oozy form. Thereafter, the ooze demon vomits on its foes, an act that revolts most foes, much to the delight of the greater ooze demon.\n\nGreater ooze demons stand 12 feet tall but can reach heights of 20 feet or more." compset="Race">
