  <thing id="rauDvHsOlH" name="Oily Hide" description="Hellstokers do not secrete oil naturally, but their constant contact with it leaves them coated with a thick layer of the substance at all times. This grants hellstokers a +10 racial bonus to Escape Artist checks (included in the statistics block). The oil cannot be washed off or removed.\n\nAdditionally, if a hellstoker is hit with a fire effect, it bursts into flames." compset="RaceSpec">
