  <thing id="rauDrMsBoB" name="Boiling Bite" description="At old age, a mist dragon&apos;s bite deals an additional 2d6 points of fire damage. An ancient dragon&apos;s damage increases to 4d6, and a great wrym&apos;s to 6d6." compset="RaceSpec">
