  <thing id="rauFnWMdPr" name="Mind Probe" description="As a full-round action, a fen witch can peer into the mind of a living creature within 60 feet in an attempt to extract the creature&apos;s true name. The target can resist the mental trespassing by succeeding on a DC 15 Will save. If the save fails, the fen witch has learned the creature&apos;s true name and can use her death speak ability. Creatures with an Intelligence score of 2 or less and creatures with no Intelligence score are immune to this ability. Psionic creatures can use defense modes or other psionic abilities to counter this probe. A creature that successfully saves cannot be affected again by the same fen witch&apos;s mind probe for one day. The save DC is Wisdom-based." compset="RaceSpec">
