  <thing id="rauFleaAtt" name="Attach" description="If a giant flea hits with a touch attack, it uses its many legs to attach itself to the opponent&apos;s body. While attached the giant flea loses its Dexterity bonus to AC and has an AC of 13. It gains a +12 racial bonus to CMD checks while attached. An attached flea can be struck with a weapon or removed by an opposed CMB attack to pluck it free. On a critical failure (a roll of 1) the flea&apos;s head snaps off in the victim and continues to drain blood for 1d8 more rounds. The head can be removed with a successful DC 18 Heal check." compset="RaceSpec">
