    </thing>
  <thing id="rauGallTZo" name="Gallows Tree Zombie" description="Each gallows tree has several gallows tree zombies connected to it. A Huge gallows tree may have no more than 7 gallows tree zombies connected to it at one time. A Gargantuan gallows tree can have a maximum of 11 zombies connected to it at any given time. See the gallows tree zombie entry in this book for details on that monster." compset="RaceSpec">
