  <thing id="ruGhoulDus" name="Ghoul, Dust" description="When a humanoid creature dies on the Parched Expanse on the Plane of Molten Fire, there is a good chance it returns from the afterlife as a dust ghoul-an undead flesh-eating creature composed of dust and earth.\n\nDust ghouls haunt the Parched Expanse, preying on unwary travelers who linger too long in their hunting grounds. These creatures savor the taste of human flesh and devour such a kill with great ferocity.\n\nDust ghouls predicate their arrival by animating dust into ghostly humanoids that immediately move to grapple potential prey. Dust ghouls then move in (often swooping in from above) and attempt to paralyze their foes with their shriek. Prey is then torn to pieces by the dust ghouls using its claws and fangs. If a dust ghoul is slain, it crumbles into a pile of dust." compset="Race">
