  <thing id="rauGlFgImM" name="Immunity to Magic" description="A flagstone golem is immune to any spell or spell-like ability that allows spell resistance. In addition, certain spells and effects function differently against the creature, as noted below.\n\n      A transmute rock to mud spell slows it (as the slow spell) for 2d6 rounds, with no saving throw.\n      A transmute mud to rock spell heals all its lost hit points.\n      A stone to flesh spell does not actually change the golem&apos;s structure, but it negates the flagstone golem&apos;s damage reduction for 1 round." compset="RaceSpec">
