  <thing id="rauGolGlTr" name="Transparent" description="A gelatinous golem is hard to see, even under ideal conditions, and it takes a DC 15 Perception check to notice one. Creatures who fail to notice a gelatinous golem and walk into it are automatically grappled (if the golem chooses to grapple the opponent)." compset="RaceSpec">
