  <thing id="rauGolIMBL" name="Bladed Lid" description="A living creature inside an iron maiden when the lid is closed is pierced by twenty dagger-like blades, dealing a total of 50 points of piercing damage each round. The lid automatically seals with an arcane lock spell with a caster level equal to that of the iron maiden golem&apos;s creator (14th level usually). The lid can be forced open with a successful Strength check (DC 34) or by casting dispel magic. The knock spell has no effect on the lid. The check DC is Strength-based and includes a +10 bonus from the arcane lock spell.\n\nBecause of the shape of the iron maiden, only a Medium humanoid can be sealed inside." compset="RaceSpec">
    <fieldval field="abDC" value="10"/>
