  <thing id="rauGlWDRsM" name="Resist Magic" description="A witch-doll golem gains a +4 bonus on all saving throws against any spell or spell-like ability or effect cast by its programmed target (provided the effect gets past its immunity to magic). The witch-doll does not have to be linked to its target to gain this bonus." compset="RaceSpec">
