  <thing id="rauGymBrSt" name="Breath Stealing" description="A slinker can suck the air from a living victim&apos;s lungs as a full-round action against any helpless opponent. The victim must succeed on a DC 11 Fortitude save. If the save fails, it takes 1d4 points of Constitution damage. At Con 0, the victim dies. The save DC is Constitution-based." compset="RaceSpec">
