oducts are highly sought after by all manner of poison-using races.\n\nAn important aspect of any inphidian community is religion. The inphidian race as a whole worships the Great Serpent (Hassith-Kaa). Little is known of this religion or the priests of the Great Serpent. Inphidian clerics can choose from any of the two following domains: Evil, Serpent, Strength, and Trickery." compset="Race">
