  <thing id="ruMoonDog" name="Moon Dog" description="The moon dog is a large wolfhound from the outer planes (believed to have its origins on the plane of Elysium). Moon dogs often enter the Material Plane when evil has grown to an immeasurable level in an area. Otherwise, they are found in the employ of deities, solars, planetars, and the most powerful devas. Moondogs forepaws are prehensile and resemble human hands. Though moon dogs can move on two legs in a bipedal fashion, most do not do so, preferring the speed and grace they gain by moving on all fours.\n\nA moon dog attacks with its powerful bite. If faced by particularly powerful or evil opponents, the moon dog opens combat with its bay attack. Moon dogs&apos; prehensile hands could facilitate the use of weapons, though none have ever been encountered wielding such items.\n\nA moon dog&apos;s natural weapons, as well as any weapons it wields, are treated as good-aligned for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction." compset="Race">
