  <thing id="rauMnDgBay" name="Bay" description="A moon dog can produce one of the following effects when it howls or barks. Each effect functions as the spell of the same name (caster level 12th). The save DCs are Charisma-based.\n\n{i}Fear:{/i} All evil creatures within 80 feet must make a successful Will save or be affected as by a fear spell. This is a sonic, mind-affecting fear effect. If the save is successful, that creature cannot be affected by the fear effect of that moon dog&apos;s bay for 24 hours.\n\n{i}Dispel Evil:{/i} This effect works like the spell, and affects one evil extraplanar creature within 80 feet.\n\n{i}Dismissal:{/i} This effect works as the spell, except that it targets one evil extraplanar creature." compset="RaceSpec">
