  <thing id="rauMCyCrSp" name="Create Spawn" description="Any living creature slain by a mortuary cyclone&apos;s necrocone attack or energy drain attack becomes an undead creature in 1d4 rounds. Spawn are under the command of the mortuary cyclone that created them and remain enslaved until its destruction.\n\nThe type of creature spawned is based on the slain creature&apos;s HD: Less than 10 HD- Zombie or skeleton, 11-15 HD-Wraith, 16-20 HD-Spectre, 21+ HD-Dread wraith" compset="RaceSpec">
