  <thing id="rauNazRage" name="Rage" description="Three times per day, a nazalor can whip itself into a maddening frenzy. As long as it rages it gains +4 Strength, +4 Constitution, and -2 AC. This rage lasts up to 1 minute, but the nazalor can end it early if desired. It is not fatigued when its rage ends." compset="RaceSpec" summary="+4 Str, +4 Con, -2 to AC when enraged.">
