  <thing id="rauNilnDrF" name="Drowning Fog" description="Once per day, a niln can create a muggy, vaporous cloud centered on its form. The cloud lasts for 1 minute (10 rounds) before dispersing, but otherwise functions as a fog cloud spell.\n\nThe muggy vapors fill the lungs of any creature in the area with water. A creature that takes only a move action can hold its breath for 2 rounds per point of Constitution; a creature that takes any action other than a move action can hold its breath for 1 round per point of Constitution. After that, refer to the rules for drowning." compset="RaceSpec">
