  <thing id="rauOakShil" name="Shillelagh" description="Any oaken club or staff wielded by an oakman automatically gains the benefits of the shillelagh spell (caster level 5th). The oakman does not have to cast this spell to get the benefit; its effects are automatic as long as the club or staff is in the oakman&apos;s hands. (This benefit is already included in the statistics block above.) In anyone else&apos;s hands, the oaken club or staff functions as a normal weapon of whatever type it is." compset="RaceSpec">
