  <thing id="rauObMImmM" name="Immunity to Magic" description="An obsidian minotaur is immune to any spell or spell-like ability that allows spell resistance. In addition, certain spells and effects function differently against the creature as noted below.\n\nA transmute rock to mud spell slows it (as the slow spell) for 2d6 rounds, with no saving throw, while transmute mud to rock heals all of its hit points.\n\nA stone to flesh spell does not actually change the obsidian minotaur&apos;s structure but negates its damage reduction and immunity to magic for 1 full round." compset="RaceSpec">
