  <thing id="rauOxDeOnB" name="Onyx Bite" description="An onyx deer&apos;s bite deals 1d4 points of Constitution damage against a living creature if it fails a DC 18 Fortitude save. A living creature reduced to Constitution 3 or less transforms into onyx, resembling nothing more than a statue. A stone to flesh spell returns a transformed creature to its original form, though if it was reduced to Constitution 0 by the onyx deer&apos;s bite it immediately dies upon returning to its natural form. The save DC is Constitution-based." compset="RaceSpec">
