  <thing id="rauAmbInfu" name="Infuse" description="A victim that has ingested an amber ooze must succeed on a DC 13 Fortitude save or the amber ooze infuses itself into his body. The ooze merges with flesh and bone, and can only be removed by a remove disease spell. The save DC is Constitution-based. A detect magic (or similar magic) cast on the host reveals the amber ooze.\n\nIf the victim succeeds on the Fortitude save, the amber ooze takes 1 point of acid damage per round from the host&apos;s digestive juices. Once it begins to take damage, the ooze retreats from the host&apos;s body through its mouth." compset="RaceSpec">
