  <thing id="rauAmbWekW" name="Weaken Will" description="An amber ooze that has infused itself into a host weakens the will of its victim. As long as the amber ooze remains in the host, he takes a -4 penalty on Will saves to resist mind-influencing spells and effects (such as charm person and suggestion.)" compset="RaceSpec">
