  <thing id="rauQuUstFo" name="Unstable Form" description="A quantum has a deflection bonus to its Armor Class equal to its Charisma bonus. Further, because it moves by means of short-distance teleportation, attacks aimed at a quantum have a 20% miss chance." compset="RaceSpec">
