  <thing id="rauSkStRag" name="Rage" description="A skin stitcher that takes damage in combat has a 50% chance of flying into a berserk rage the following round, attacking its foe until either it or its opponent is dead. It gains +4 Strength and -4 AC while raging. The skin stitcher cannot end its rage voluntarily. Note that the skin stitcher does not drop its chains while raging." compset="RaceSpec" summary="+4 Str, -2 to AC when enraged.">
