  <thing id="ruHeatSwar" name="Heat Swarm" description="A heat swarm is a mass of flying, aggressive, foul-tempered elementals from the Para-Plane of Heat. A single heat elemental that makes up a heat swarm resembles a thumb-sized ball of fire with vaguely discernable facial features.\n\nHeat swarms are highly territorial and attack any creatures (other than their own kind) entering their domain. Several swarms often work together to drive away a common foe.\n\nWhen encountered on the Material Plane (which is a very rare occurrence indeed), a heat swarm is most often found in a highly unbearable (by human standards) climate such as an active volcano.\n\nA heat swarm attacks by moving on top of and engulfing its foe." compset="Race">
