  <thing id="rauTshBurr" name="Burrow" description="A t&apos;shann rarely appears in the open air, preferring the closeness and coolness of being deep in the earth. In order to attack a t&apos;shann physically, an opponent must first find it and lure it out of its burrow. Finding a t&apos;shann burrow requires a successful DC 15 Perception check. Once the burrow is located, the t&apos;shann can be lured out by placing small pile of gems at the entrance. The t&apos;shann must succeed on a DC 10 Will save or shuffle out of its lair to consume the treats." compset="RaceSpec">
