  <thing id="rauTntHrHo" name="Horn" description="The source of a tentacled horror&apos;s power is its horn. If a tentacled horror&apos;s horn is removed, it loses its regeneration ability and suffers a –6 penalty to Strength and Constitution until the horn is reattached. The horn is AC 20, hardness 10, and has 20 hit points. A tentacled horror&apos;s horn cannot be removed unless it is helpless. It takes a successful DC 40 Strength or 10 points of damage to the horn to remove a tentacled horror&apos;s horn." compset="RaceSpec">
