  <thing id="rauTFlyRel" name="Reality Bend" description="As a free action, a time flayer can fold the dimensional space surrounding it so its true location is hard to discern. Attackers have a 50% miss chance each time they attack with melee or ranged weapons. This is similar to the miss chance granted by a displacement spell. See invisibility does not reveal the creature&apos;s location, but true seeing does." compset="RaceSpec">
