  <thing id="rauTriFlui" name="Fluid Drain" description="Against a sleeping or helpless foe, a tri-flower frond can release a needle-sharp tendril from its red bloom that pierces its target and drains its body fluids. This deals 1d4 points of Constitution damage each round, and the victim is considered grappled." compset="RaceSpec">
