  <thing id="rauSTShSmG" name="Smite Good" description="Once per day, a stygian turtle-shark can smite a good-aligned foe. The turtle adds its Charisma bonus (if any) to its attack rolls and adds its total HD to all damage rolls made against the target of her smite. Regardless of the target, smite evil attacks automatically bypass any DR the creature might possess." compset="RaceSpec" summary="+CHA to hit and +HD to melee damage against targeted good creature.">
