  <thing id="rauWzSAtta" name="Attach" description="If a wizard&apos;s shackle hits with a bite attack, it latches onto the opponent&apos;s body. An attached wizard&apos;s shackle is effectively grappling its prey. The wizard&apos;s shackle loses its Dexterity bonus to AC and has an AC of 14, but holds on with great tenacity. Wizard&apos;s shackles have a +20 racial bonus on grapple checks.\n\nAn attached wizard&apos;s shackle can be struck with a weapon or grappled itself. To remove an attached wizard&apos;s shackle through grappling, the opponent must achieve a pin against the wizard&apos;s shackle." compset="RaceSpec">
