  <thing id="rauGiCFren" name="Frenzy" description="A giant caribe that detects blood in the water goes into a killing frenzy, as do all other giant caribes within a 90-foot radius. Frenzied giant caribes attack until either they or their opponents are dead.\n\nA frenzied giant caribe can make one extra attack when making a full attack action. The attack is made using the creature&apos;s full base attack. Additionally, it gains a +1 bonus on attack rolls and a +1 dodge bonus to AC and Reflex saves. A frenzied giant caribe&apos;s swim speed increases by 10 feet. This frenzy lasts for 1 minute and can only be used once per encounter." compset="RaceSpec">
