    </thing>
  <thing id="rauDbFDefT" name="Defiling Touch" description="The damage dealt by a debased fey&apos;s natural attacks resists all magical healing (though it can be healed normally through rest). A creature attempting to cast a cure spell or a heal spell on a creature damaged by a debased fey&apos;s natural attacks must make a successful caster level check (DC 10 + 1/2 the debased fey&apos;s HD + the debased fey&apos;s Constitution modifier, +2 racial bonus), or the spell has no effect on the injured creature." compset="RaceSpec">
