  <thing id="rauDbFAnat" name="Anathema" description="A debased fey has been rejected by the purity of nature. Normal plants within 20 feet wither and die if the debased fey remains in proximity for more than 5 minutes. Pure environments such as untouched forests and clear streams and ponds may become spoiled and polluted if the debased fey remains in that environment for more than 1 day.\n\nPlant creatures (such as shambling mounds, for example) take 1d2 points of damage each round they remain within 20 feet of a debased fey. A Fortitude save negates the damage for that round. A new save can be made each round." compset="RaceSpec">
    <usesource source="srcTomeHor"/>
    <tag group="StandardDC" tag="aCHA"/>
