  <thing id="rauPalPrmR" name="Primal Roar" description="A paleoskeleton can, once every other round, unleash an eerie roar. Creatures with fewer Hit Dice than the paleoskeleton must succeed on a Will save or be shaken for 2d6 rounds." compset="RaceSpec">
