  <thing id="rauPhEthJa" name="Ethereal Jaunt" description="A phase creature can shift from the Ethereal to the Material Plane as a free action, and shift back again as a move action (or during a move action). The ability is otherwise identical with ethereal jaunt (caster level 15th)." compset="RaceSpec">
