  <thing id="rauPhEthAm" name="Ethereal Ambush" description="A phase creature that attacks foes on the Material Plane in a surprise round can take a full round of actions if it begins the combat by phasing into the Material Plane from the Ethereal Plane." compset="RaceSpec">
