  <thing id="rcuTheSckG" name="Sickness Gaze" description="A creature within 30 feet that meets the therianthrope&apos;s gaze is sickened for a number of rounds equal to 3 + the therianthrope&apos;s HD (maximum 10 rounds). Affected creatures can attempt a Fortitude save to avoid the effects. Creatures that successfully save cannot be affected by that therianthrope&apos;s gaze for one day. A delay poison or neutralize poison spell removes the effects from the sickened creature. Creatures that are immune to poison are unaffected, and creatures resistant to poison receive their normal bonus on their saving throw. A therianthrope is immune to its own sickness gaze and the sickness gaze of other therianthropes of the same base animal type." compset="RaceCustom" uniqueness="useronce">
