  <thing id="rcuTheSlpG" name="Sleep Gaze" description="Any creature within 30 feet that meets the creature&apos;s gaze falls asleep for a number of minutes equal to the therianthrope&apos;s HD if it fails a Will save. This ability functions as the sleep spell (caster level equals therianthrope&apos;s HD), but it can affect creatures of any Hit Dice. A therianthrope is immune to its own sleep gaze and the sleep gaze of other therianthropes of the same base animal type." compset="RaceCustom" uniqueness="useronce">
