  <thing id="rcuTheWeak" name="Weakness Gaze" description="Any creature within 30 feet that meets the creature&apos;s gaze takes 1d4+1 points of Strength or Dexterity damage. A successful Fortitude save negates the damage. This ability can be used twice per day and one more time per day per 5 HD of the therianthrope. A therianthrope is immune to its own weakness gaze and the weakness gaze of other therianthropes of the same base animal type." compset="RaceCustom" uniqueness="useronce">
